$PROBLEM Dual Numbers benchmark - NONMEM
$ABBREVIATED DERIV2=NO
$INPUT ID TIME AMT DV WT
$DATA ..\..\data\sim_0_0_0_0.csv IGNORE=@
;; data file name must match out file name in the template file for simulations in data folder
;;from data\template.txt
;; $TABLE ID TIME AMT IOBS EVID WT FILE=c:\git\dual_numbers\data\OUT_0_0_0_0.DAT NOPRINT NOHEADER NOAPPEND
;; and file read/write in make_data.r
;; file_name <- paste0(this_comp,"_",this_eta,"_",this_vwt,"_",this_gamma)
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN6 TOL=7
$MODEL COMP=(DEPOT,DEFDOSE) COMP=(CENTRAL,NODOSE,DEFOBS)
$PK
CWT = WT/70
TVVMAX= THETA(1)
VMAX=TVVMAX*EXP(ETA(1))
TVKM = THETA(2)
KM = TVKM
TVV2=THETA(3)
V2=TVV2
TVKA=THETA(4)
KA=TVKA
SC = V2
$ERROR REP = IREP IPRED = F
Y=F*EXP(EPS(2)) + EPS(1)
$DES
CONC = A(2)/SC
DADT(1) = -KA*A(1)
DADT(2) = KA*A(1)-VMAX*CONC/(KM+CONC)
$THETA (100,1670,3000) ; THETA(1) VMAX UNITS = mass/time
(100,1200,3000) ; THETA(2) KM UNITS = mass/volume
(1,12,40) ; THETA(3) V UNITS = volume
(0.01,0.917,3) ; THETA(4) KA UNITS = 1/time
;; Start OMEGA
$OMEGA 0.121 ; ETA(1) ETA ON VMAX
$SIGMA 412 ; ; EPS(1) ADDITIVE
0.275 ; _ ; EPS(2) PROPORTIONAL
;;$ESTIMATION METHOD=COND INTER MAXEVALS=9999 NOHABORT NOOMEGABOUNDTEST
;; NOSIGMABOUNDTEST NOTHETABOUNDTEST
;;$COVARIANCE UNCOND PRECOND=2
;;; Model Identifier = 0,0,0,0
;; Phenotype: ([('COMP', 0), ('ETAs', 0), ('V~WT', 0), ('GAMMA', 0)])
;; Genotype: [0, 0, 0, 0]
;; Num non-influential tokens: 0
$SIM ONLYSIM (1233) SUBPROB = 200 $TABLE ID TIME DV MDV NOPRINT NOHEADER NOAPPEND FILE=OBS_DAT $TABLE ID REP TIME DV IPRED PRED MDV NOPRINT NOHEADER NOAPPEND FILE=SIM_DAT
